&lt;p&gt;The Narrative Editing team owns the collection of product experiences that enable creators to tell their story. The team owns Descript’s flagship script-based editing experience, which changed the landscape of video editing tools by making storytelling-based content creation accessible to beginner creators, and lightning-fast for experts. While AI-based video editing has provided optionality to creators across all parts of the Descript product, this team has the unique opportunity to partner closely with AI infrastructure and research teams to evaluate, integrate, and operate both internal and external models that make it even easier and faster for creators to produce high caliber content.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Narrative Editing team’s focus in 2026 is to take great product experiences and make them even better for our customers. If you’re passionate about not just building the V0 of products, but the V1, V2, V3, and beyond, this role is a great fit for you!&lt;/p&gt;
