&lt;li&gt;Driving execution on strategic quality initiatives alongside building the next iteration of product experiences in Descript&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partnering with AI Research and Enablement teams to prioritize, train, evaluate, and deliver the next generation of Descript-built AI models that power content creation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
